<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In the file Zend/Di/InstanceManager.php line 280 character 92 there should have been 2 rather than 3.</p>

<p>Currently, when creating a new instance using <code>createInstanceViaConstructor</code> in case count($callParameters) is 3, the returned value is:
new $class($callParameters[0], $callParameters[1], $callParameters[3])
which is obviously wrong and should be:
new $class($callParameters[0], $callParameters[1], $callParameters[2])</p>

